# ProwlrBot website — optional auth (Clerk)
# Copy to .env.local and set VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY to enable Log in / Sign up on the site.
# Get your key at https://dashboard.clerk.com
# Local/dev:  VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
# Production: use pk_live_... and set it in Cloudflare Pages → prowlrbot → Settings → Environment variables (Production)
# VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
